sequenceDiagram
    Client->>+LoadBalancer: HTTPS GET /
    LoadBalancer->>+NGINX: HTTP(Infra_IngressController) GET /
    loop route
        NGINX ->> NGINX: Route based on Host/ServerAlias
    end
    NGINX->>+Webservice: HTTP GET /
    Webservice->>-NGINX: HTTP 302/200 (Infra_LoadBalancer)
    NGINX->>-LoadBalancer: HTTP 302/200 (Infra_WorkerNode)
    LoadBalancer->>-Client: HTTP 302/200 (Infra_RedisCache)
